Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.05,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.66,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I was just tagging along with my Aunt Kazuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've caused all kinds of problems\nfor my aunt for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.89,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,so that was the least I could do for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.13,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,More importantly, go ahead and sign the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to get out\nof hikikomori, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how, once you sign the contract, Sato-kun!
