Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know how old I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.81,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I... I'd guess around 17 or 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.58,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, you're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.26,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up, Sato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.79,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you're going to regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:51.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This could be your last chance, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at the same\ntime tomorrow, okay?
