Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:37.30,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,How long am I going to repeat days like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.81,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,A long time ago, I read a sci-fi novel like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:50.78,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,The story takes place in the near future, after the\nhuman race is annihilated in the final war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.26,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,The main character is the only survivor.
