Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.77,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So they create a simulation of\NEarth as it had been,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:10.97,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,and try to hide the truth that mankind\nhad been wiped out from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.75,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,However, if he were to spend too much\ntime outside of his house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:20.01,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,he would figure out that the world he lives in is a fake.
