Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:04.28,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-san, can we talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:07.25,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,We know you're in there! Please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:11.79,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of your hikikomori condition,\nan innocent young girl has been deeply scarred!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.22,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to apologize to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.54,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx73.75\fscy48.75\frx0\fry42\frz64.553\pos(207,181)\c&H1E1E59&\3c&HEAC69C&\4c&HEAC69C&}BEWARE OF MOLESTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.54,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx73.75\fscy48.75\frx0\fry42\frz53.44\pos(178,129)\c&H3C2F1A&\3c&HEAC69C&\4c&HEAC69C&}\NCall 110 if you spot\nsuspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,There she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:52.13,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're an hour late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.89,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You... What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.83,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a sweet little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.57,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,who's willing to rescue a hikikomori loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:04.24,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm not hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:09.08,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It was quite obvious when my aunt and I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But I told you guys that I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.72,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But normally people wouldn't get flustered\nlike that unless they are hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.42,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you bring the contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.95,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:25.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You come to this park every Sunday night and\ndo nothing but gaze into space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.39,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But other than that, you don't go outside at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\nthat's a hikikomori condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:36.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's... it's true that I'm always in my apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.83,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but I can't help it because of my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.58,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What is your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.41,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.64,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,SOHO...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.11,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,SOHO?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It means "small office home office"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:51.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm working from home,\nso it's not like I'm unemployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:55.19,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But you came to the coffee shop for a job interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:59.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I just did that on a whim! That was an impulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.56,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of job do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.60,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.96,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I said, don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:20.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Since my job requires me to be creative,\NI may come off sort of weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:25.25,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but that's just an aspect of my brilliant talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.32,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So, what do you create?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.69,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.82,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,the most advanced, revolutionary IT...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.40,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! It's computer-related!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.03,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Software development, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:42.66,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm in the middle of making software!\NIt's so awesome it'd put even Bill or Linus to shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Be sure to bring the contract tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.03,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.95,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:59.62,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}For some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}The cell phone isnt enough for girls to go on with their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:05.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}The cell phone isnt enough for girls to go on with their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.83,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,"Bring it tomorrow,' my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:18.97,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}It's important that her heart swells with love and courage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare she look at me like she's\nsome kind of know-it-all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got a computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:16.14,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I could easily write a program or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:22.24,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}I am pururin purupururin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,SHUT THE HELL UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}Pururin purupururin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:31.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}Rinrin purupuru pururin pururu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.29,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Today is the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.75,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not going to put up with this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}Its soft like a marshmallow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}My eyes get teary
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:44.05,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}A magical girl of dreams and hopes, dreams and hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}A magical girl of dreams and hopes, dreams and hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.30,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}A magical girl of dreams and hopes, dreams and hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,HEY, COME OUT NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.96,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,IF YOU DON'T COME OUT,\NI'LL BREAK IT DOWN MYSELF!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:52.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Turn that shit down\NTurn off that goddamn anime song!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Sato-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:06.38,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this for real? Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:14.33,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're the anime otaku\nwho moved in next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.73,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:25.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H363B41&\3c&HAAB6BA&\4a&HFF&\frx2\fry314\pos(169,121)\frz280.171\fscx132.5\fscy130}LITERATURE CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H002231&\3c&HA9B9C0&\4a&HFF&\frx336\fry314\fscx56.25\fscy80\pos(86,63)\frz335.279}Tea Ceremony Club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.35,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Join the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:35.95,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\4a&HFF&\frz21.434\c&H3C403A&\3c&HDDE3DE&\pos(260,108)\fscx131.25\fscy216.25\frx18\fry320\bord2}CULTURAL CLUBS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:36.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Those few words made me decide to spend my\nthree high school years in the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:41.82,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course, I had no interest in novels whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.53,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So, my daily club activities were playing cards\nand hanging out with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:49.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,listening to her bizarre conspiracy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.30,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez, what the hell was I doing back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.67,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure there were lots of other things\NI could have been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Two years rolled by very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And one day, shortly before her graduation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:09.12,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.81,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's bullying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.69,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Should I go help the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.69,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.96,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, they're just middle school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:23.39,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Bullying is not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Quickly the hunter became the hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.01,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She was amazed how pathetic I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:38.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but supposedly the guy being bullied\nwas deeply moved by my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.28,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H303637&\3c&HCAD3D9&\4a&HFF&\pos(178,124)\fscx162.5\fscy118.75\frz275.827}LITERATURE CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:44.97,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H002231&\3c&HA9B9C0&\4a&HFF&\frx336\fry314\fscx56.25\fscy80\pos(86,63)\frz335.279}Tea Ceremony Club
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like to join the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That was Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:55.73,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Four years after my graduation,\nthis is an unexpected reunion indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.67,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's messy. Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.96,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:12.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Who would've thought the anime song\nfreak next door was Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.22,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry about the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.42,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess the walls of this apartment\nare pretty thin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:21.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usually, people would realize stuff like that\na few days after they moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.35,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H30&}Besides, I've been listening to it every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H30&}I guess I've become numb to the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.16,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't realize you live right next door to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but I always knew that you'd go\nto college in Tokyo though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.67,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This is your fourth year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.13,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Y... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:35.84,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been going to a vocational school\nin Tokyo since this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.97,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I was looking for an apartment that's\neasy to commute from and cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I found this place and I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HCBA77D&\bord2\4a&HFF&\frz337.701\fscx53.75\fscy80\pos(257,200)}School Rules
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz334.654\4a&HFF&\pos(218,131)\c&H4B0BC7&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx71.25\fscy72.5}Thunder{\c&H000000&}bolt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz230.477\c&H954FDB&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4a&HFF&\fscx73.75\fscy66.25\pos(28,42)}ESPer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.28,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HAD89FF&\3c&HE5FFFF&\4a&HFF&\bord3\frz331.442\fscx170\fscy157.5\move(28,125,6,122)}Cat\NEar
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.28,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HAD89FF&\3c&HE5FFFF&\4a&HFF&\bord3\frz331.442\fscx147.5\fscy357.5\move(78,158,49,160)}Quarted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.28,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H60FFF7&\3c&H546174&\4a&HFF&\bord2\fscx103.75\fscy86.25\frz48.086\move(172,203,146,202)}Potato Digging Club
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:49.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I was already predicting that he'd probably\nend up like this four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:59.85,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So, have you been bullied at the\nschool you go to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:04.40,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You were crying earlier, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.47,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,People in my class are nothing but morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.51,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They don't know a thing about video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:15.24,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But they all act like they know\nwhat they're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Girls are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:21.55,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I just wanna ask them why they even\nbother coming to the school at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,At this rate, there's no hope for the future\nof Japan's video game industry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.46,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Up we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.05,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.24,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.44,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.42,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.56,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Seriously, it was so much fun back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:09.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish those carefree days had never ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.20,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.24,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFDF7FF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz13.066\fscx61.25\fscy71.25\pos(221,180)}Game Creator Department
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.24,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFDF7FF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz14.525\fscx46.25\fscy65\pos(230,213)}Kokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.67,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Designer Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:23.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, haven't you seen the TV commercial before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been going to the\NGame Creator Department of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\4a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFEFAFF&\frz14.278\q2\fscx207.5\fscy230\pos(179,81)}Game Creator Department
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\4a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFEFAFF&\frz14.883\fscx155\fscy173.75\pos(204,195)}Kokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Game Creator Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:40.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, can I borrow this?
