Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.60,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right on time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.47,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you bring the contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What I told you last night wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:03.12,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I graduated from the Game Creator\NDepartment of a design institute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.35,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This book looks like it's brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.09,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I only have to read things once\nto get the general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been that way all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What does "object-oriented" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:19.66,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, now you understand that\NI'm a creator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Then will you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.74,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,The game you've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:32.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HD6B29D&\4a&HFF&\bord2\c&H4E51A2&\q2\frz269.041\fscx296.25\fscy312.5\move(157,-20,149,285,10,6350)}BEWARE OF MOLESTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:32.89,nhk,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:32.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HD6B29D&\4a&HFF&\bord2\q2\frz269.041\move(138,31,129,285,10,6350)\c&H00000A&}Call 110 if you spot suspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:31.08,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's not finished yet, and I'm not supposed\nto show it to the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:32.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Your graduation project would do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's just junk that I made before I became a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.12,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So anything but that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.75,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You are very gifted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:47.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If... If you insist, fine, I'll show it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,My masterpiece from the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But not right away though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.40,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't even remember where I put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And besides, I'm busy with some of my\nmost important work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.34,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It'd probably be sometime next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, next month then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.97,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.35,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:18.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Y... Yamazaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:22.36,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a college-dropout and have been\nhikikomori for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.10,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Who would've thought that you're a NEET?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:29.07,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that, you told such a huge\nlie just to impress a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:32.07,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It kinda slipped out on the spur of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.54,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Yamazaki,\NI have a little favor to ask of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:39.81,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're thinking about asking me to lend you\na game I've made, forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.55,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I just started classes at that school myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.75,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have anything that's decent\nenough to let you borrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.46,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna try to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.10,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,A game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:56.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And not just to show off for some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:20:00.33,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If you succeed, you might be able to\nrecover from being a NEET!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.87,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And gaining experience is beneficial for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.47,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to make a game together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.38,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:12.51,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, what kind of skills do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:18.32,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,For example, can you draw, or\nmake music or program?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:21.12,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm totally hopeless when it\ncomes to stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.39,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So, that means scripting the scenario is\nabout the only think you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.69,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the scriptwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:30.40,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, hell no, I haven't "composed" anything\nsince I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.73,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But you were in the Literature Club, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.60,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Think about this. Have you ever read\nany novel written by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,First of all writing stuff is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.64,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you wanna do this or not?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.81,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:50.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though he's a wuss, he can be\nshort-tempered and very argumentative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.35,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he was bullied to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:54.46,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.48,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I should be able to come up with\nsomething for the scenario!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.53,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Good, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:03.26,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Now the problem is time, since you promised her\nthat you were going to show it to her next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.60,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if we had a little bit more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.44,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Is making a game such a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.57,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.07,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,When it comes to a big project, it usually\ntakes a few of years to produce it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,a several hundred people to work on it\nand hundreds of billion yen to fund it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.51,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,However, there are people out there\nwith no money or help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:23.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They can't even program anything decent,\nand all they have is some crappy music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.32,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,However, even if one's situation is that miserable,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:29.46,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,there's a certain game genre that still\nallows you to produce a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,and if you're lucky, get rich quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's awesome, Yamazaki! That is it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.36,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But this road will be difficult and\npainted in our sweat and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:41.14,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't tell me, '"You know what? I quit!"\NIn the middle of production!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.07,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.77,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So, what is the game genre you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.57,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Erotic game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
